```{r include=FALSE}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = TRUE)
```

```{r message=FALSE, warning=FALSE}
library(viridis)
```
Este codigo muestra la Magma en el paquete [viridis] (https://github.com/sjmgarnier/viridis). Muestra un mapa de contorno del volcán Maunga Whau en Auckland, Nueva Zelanda.
## Magma colors

```{r fig.cap="Volcan Maunga Whau, Auckland."}
image(volcano,col=viridis(200,option = "A"))
```
Adicionalmente vamos a explorar qué otras gamas de colores nos aporta Viridis
## Inferno colors

```{r fig.cap="Volcan Maunga Whau, Auckland."}
image(volcano,col=viridis(200,option = "B"))
```
## Plasma colors

```{r fig.cap="Volcan Maunga Whau, Auckland."}
image(volcano,col=viridis(200,option = "C"))
```
## Viridis colors

```{r fig.cap="Volcan Maunga Whau, Auckland."}
image(volcano,col=viridis(200,option = "D"))
```
## Cividis colors

```{r fig.cap="Volcan Maunga Whau, Auckland."}
image(volcano,col=viridis(200,option = "E"))
```
